marketing_&_analytics_team:
- promote products
- analyze campaigns, sales, customer behavior
- example: test ads on facebook vs instagram, choose best

product_strategy_&_planning_team:
- decide what product & features to launch
- align with market trends
- example: add ai camera after competitor trend

product_design_&_development_team:
- design look & feel of product
- develop features, software, prototypes
- example: create phone body + camera app

manufacturing_&_supply_chain_team:
- produce product at scale
- manage parts, suppliers, distribution
- example: factory builds phones, ship to amazon/retail
